# Routes
# This file defines all application routes (Higher priority routes first)
# ~~~~

### API Routes ###
GET        /api/github/json/direct        @controllers.api.GithubRest.getGithubPushEvents
POST       /api/github/json/githubEvent   @controllers.api.GithubRest.listenForGithubPushEvents

GET        /api/user        @controllers.api.UserRest.get

GET        /api/task        @controllers.api.TaskRest.get

GET        /api/todo        @controllers.api.UserRest.todo



### Web Routes ###

# Home page
GET        /        controllers.Assets.at(path="/public", file="index.html")

# Map the JS resource paths
GET        /*file        controllers.Assets.at(path="/public", file)
